# Install as /etc/exports.d/cryptowallet-netboot.exports then: sudo exportfs -rav
#
# The exported directory MUST be the same path as in boot.cmd: setenv nfsroot <this path>
#
# Typical lab: export the tree populated by create_fs.sh (no /srv copy):
/data/projects/CryptoWallet-NanoPI/infra/nanopi/netboot/nfsroot 192.168.126.0/23(rw,sync,no_subtree_check,no_root_squash)
#
# Alternative: rsync repo nfsroot to /srv/... (see setup-netboot-host.sh), export that path, and set the same path in boot.cmd:
# /srv/cryptowallet-netboot/nfsroot 192.168.126.0/23(rw,sync,no_subtree_check,no_root_squash)
